{"tid":1901190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有做過小學雞功輔興趣班導師嘅入嚟 比票你選勞工界選委","createTime":"2020-02-27T16:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T03:48:52.000Z","uid":210495,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0f45566867a3f455a58133543fb9f7a195a8d8","tid":1901190,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nvmtcys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvmtcys.jpg&h=7984a5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話說今日phonein左吳敏兒<br />\n佢confirm左一件事：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只要你有7個人</span></span></strong> 同機構 就可以組一個工會 就有一票選勞工界選委<br />\n咩意思呢<br />\n例如我係小童群x會做功輔班導師A 我有6個朋友都一齊做功輔班導師<br />\n有簽約 同小童群x會有僱佣關係<br />\n就已經可以組工會<br />\n<br />\n你要做嘅野 就要攞齊7個人嘅名同地址 仲有工作證明 例如mpf<br />\n然後填NU1籌組職工會發起人名表 同埋4(s)職工會登記申請書<br />\nNU1 form: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1_LbXjmjA1M7rvCCgNL_yPUc-FUSpBr2p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1_LbXjmjA1M7rvCCgNL_yPUc-FUSpBr2p&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=4df6c1ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1_LbXjmjA1M7rvCCgNL_yPUc-FUSpBr2p</a><br />\n4(s) form: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1iHqahOGQDzbPsOCyBw4TM-MSttQ13Zrm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1iHqahOGQDzbPsOCyBw4TM-MSttQ13Zrm&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=11a5333a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1iHqahOGQDzbPsOCyBw4TM-MSttQ13Zrm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AAcwaj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAAcwaj9.jpg&h=0c2c3fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去<a href=\"https://7up.hkpetitions.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F7up.hkpetitions.com&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=704c7e0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://7up.hkpetitions.com</a> gen會章<br />\n之後等通知<br />\n制憲後你就有票架喇！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V0Mtcyw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV0Mtcyw.jpg&h=ad7c1cc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22b4428578a8d1c4a30b4cc92ee03f5448f2dc5d","tid":1901190,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:17:36.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"15d7a85891dff09fcc0385f7356a684595891db5","tid":1901190,"uid":266286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"[其實對家唔係戇鳩] 黃圈被滲透及分化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"031812e739428c9bf3ce5dc86a5b2161692dba9a","tid":1901190,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"06078f141406146de4ef797685d49c5bd2010bad","tid":1901190,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"d372d0e8c96ecc89e6adbc1bb7f4c28d0bebf460","tid":1901190,"uid":260366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"你今日抵制咗未？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【每日任務@27/2】<br />\n💎 Pizza-Box🍕 💎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pizzaboxhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpizzaboxhk%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0ctNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=97ab58b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pizzaboxhk/</a><br />\n😡1.派嬲 🗣2.洗版 🙅🏻&zwj;♀️3.永久抵制 👍🏻4.互Like留言<br />\n2011年有14人參加派對，Pizza Box 食物懷疑導致食物中毒！👎🏻<br />\n上年11月Pizza Box 電單車喺沙田周梓樂悼念會中駛向人群，結果司機遭私了！間公司有冇管好自己員工架？👎🏻<br />\n#PizzaBox<br />\n[Source]<br />\n疑令14人食物中毒 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2T4NFgZ\" data-sr-url=\"https